A substantial literature exists in other scientific fields discussing techniques for estimating the repeatability, reliability, and accuracy of a set of measurements \citep[see, for example,][for discussions of repeatability and reliability]{Altman:1983bn,Bartlett:2008bc}.  We review and adapt these terms below.  

